[30;1m51 | [0m[35m        X = X - self.mean + self.eps[0m
[30;1m52 | [0m[35m        cov = np.cov(X.T) / X.shape[0][0m
[30;1m53 | [0m[35m        v, w = np.linalg.eig(cov)[0m
[30;1m54 | [0m[35m        idx = v.argsort()[::-1]  # Sort eigenvalues in descending order[0m
[30;1m55 | [0m[35m        v, w = v[idx], w[:, idx][0m
[30;1m56 | [0m[35m        self.w = w[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m        return self[0m
